						               													<description>Legend - The 1000 Miglia Action Game is the second title of the Legend Series, covering the historical 1000 Miglia Race. This game is intended for all those gamers looking for a historically-accurate racing game,  but also characterized by simple rules and a streamlined mechanics. In few words an action game! The real key-point of this game is the scalable rules, suitable for small kids up to experienced gamers, especially with the special dice-pack add-on available on publisher's site.&amp;#10;You will have to face critical road conditions and winding roads, struggling to get the most out of your car, yet avoiding any unnecessary damage, to finish first in Brescia after 1000 miles of racing across Italy.&amp;#10;The most appreciated elements of its &amp;quot;big bro&amp;quot; Legend - The History of 1000 Miglia are featured also in The 1000 Miglia Action Game: 19 different car models, Car Performance Cards in the same colors of the real cars' cockpits, accurate stage layouts and the expected Made in Italy quality by WBS Games.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
